name: Old New Borrowed & Blue
bio:
Based on the ol' wedding adage the show forces comics to begin with their oldest material, then switch to brand new jokes, add a borrowed bit from a favorite comedian, then close as dirty.

produced in New York by Jake Head, Shane Torres, & Ariel Elias
copy:
Held monthly at the Creek & The Cave in New York Old New Borrowed & Blue plays off the ol' wedding adage forcing comics to begin with their oldest material, then switch to brand new jokes, add a borrowed bit from a favorite comedian, then close with their dirtiest stuff.

produced by Jake Head, Shane Torres, & Ariel Elias
